asEventOccurrence

public EventText asEventOccurrence()
Deprecated. 
Returns an EventText which approximates this event phrase. The result will have the same event type as this and its EventText.getProvenanceChunks() will return a single-element set consisting of this EventPhrase itself. If this EventPhrase has non-null tense or aspect, it will be added as an attribute of the returned EventOccurrence.
